 }
 ```
+
+## Adding a downstream exporter {#module-services-prometheus-exporters-new-exporter}
+
+First create the exporter file, `exporter.nix` as you would with an upstream exporter
+
+Then create a module that imports the exporter
+
+```nix
+{ config, pkgs, lib, options, utils, ... }@args:
+
+with (import ./mk-exporter.nix lib);
+
+{
+  options.services.prometheus.exporters = mkDownstreamOptions "EXPORTER" (import ./EXPORTER.nix args);
+  config = mkDownstreamConfig "EXPORTER" (import ./EXPORTER.nix args) config.services.prometheus.exporters.EXPORTER;
+}
+```
